  <source>AstraZeneca</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to confirm the safety profile / factors which impact safety and
      efficacy of Nexium capsules in daily clinical usage for the patients who have been prescribed
      Nexium for &quot;gastric ulcer&quot;, &quot;duodenal ulcer&quot;, &quot;anastomotic ulcer&quot;, &quot;reflux oesophagitis&quot;,
      &quot;non-erosive reflux disease&quot;, or &quot;Zollinger-Ellison syndrome&quot;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Nexium capsules Clinical Experience Investigation
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
